  <title>Designing for Rehabilitation at Home Keywords Rehabilitation technologies, stroke, user centred design ACM Classification Keywords</title>
  <abstractText>New technologies open up possibilities for designing interactive experiences that can engage and motivate post-stroke survivors to undertake what would otherwise be boring repetitive movements. In this paper we outline a few of the challenges we met as part of the cross-disciplinary Motivating Mobility project. These are: the extended &apos;user&apos;; autonomy and motivation; and early prototype studies.</abstractText>
